#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:0.2"
msgid "12. Lokakāmaguṇavagga "
msgstr "12. The World and the Kinds of Sensual Stimulation "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 117. Kāmaguṇasutta → lokakāmaguṇa 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.117:0.3"
msgid "117. Kāmaguṇasutta "
msgstr "117. The Kinds of Sensual Stimulation "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.98, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.1"
msgid "“Pubbeva me, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I thought: "

msgctxt "sn35.117:1.2"
msgid "‘yeme pañca kāmaguṇā cetaso samphuṭṭhapubbā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā, tatra me cittaṃ bahulaṃ gacchamānaṃ gaccheyya paccuppannesu vā appaṃ vā anāgatesu’. "
msgstr "‘My mind might often stray towards the five kinds of sensual stimulation that I formerly experienced—which have passed, ceased, and perished—or to those in the present, or in the future a little.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to me: "

# NOTE: See my note on attarupa at an 4.117
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.4"
msgid "‘yeme pañca kāmaguṇā cetaso samphuṭṭhapubbā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā, tatra me attarūpena appamādo sati cetaso ārakkho karaṇīyo’. "
msgstr "‘In my own way I should practice diligence, mindfulness, and protecting the mind regarding the five kinds of sensual stimulation that I formerly experienced—which have passed, ceased, and perished.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.5"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, tumhākampi ye te pañca kāmaguṇā cetaso samphuṭṭhapubbā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā, tatra vo cittaṃ bahulaṃ gacchamānaṃ gaccheyya paccuppannesu vā appaṃ vā anāgatesu. "
msgstr "So, mendicants, your minds might also often stray towards the five kinds of sensual stimulation that you formerly experienced—which have passed, ceased, and perished—or to those in the present, or in the future a little. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:1.6"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, tumhākampi ye te pañca kāmaguṇā cetaso samphuṭṭhapubbā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā, tatra vo attarūpehi appamādo sati cetaso ārakkho karaṇīyo. "
msgstr "So in your own way you should practice diligence, mindfulness, and protecting the mind regarding the five kinds of sensual stimulation that I formerly experienced—which have passed, ceased, and perished. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
# NOTE: See BB’s notes on grammar and readings, which I follow.
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.7"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr "So you should understand that dimension where the eye ceases and perception of sights fades away. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:1.8"
msgid "yattha jivhā ca nirujjhati, rasasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr "You should understand that dimension where the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.117:1.9"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe”ti. "
msgstr "mind ceases and perception of thoughts fades away.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:1.10"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā bhagavā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ pāvisi. "
msgstr "When he had spoken, the Holy One got up from his seat and entered his dwelling. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.117:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ acirapakkantassa bhagavato etadahosi: "
msgstr "Soon after the Buddha left, those mendicants considered, "

msgctxt "sn35.117:2.2"
msgid "“idaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr "“The Buddha gave this brief summary, then entered his dwelling without explaining the meaning in detail. … "

msgctxt "sn35.117:2.3"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:2.4"
msgid "yattha jivhā ca nirujjhati, rasasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:2.5"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:2.6"
msgid "Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā”ti? "
msgstr "Who can explain in detail the meaning of this brief summary given by the Buddha?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn35.117:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then those mendicants thought, "

msgctxt "sn35.117:3.2"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho āyasmā ānando satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito, sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. "
msgstr "“This Venerable Ānanda is praised by the Buddha and esteemed by his sensible spiritual companions. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:3.3"
msgid "Pahoti cāyasmā ānando imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajituṃ. "
msgstr "He is capable of explaining in detail the meaning of this brief summary given by the Buddha. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:3.4"
msgid "Yannūna mayaṃ yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkameyyāma; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāmā”ti. "
msgstr "Let’s go to him, and ask him about this matter.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.99, sc4
msgctxt "sn35.117:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu. "
msgstr "Then those mendicants went to Ānanda, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:4.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they sat down to one side. They told him what had happened, and said, "

#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn35.117:5.1"
msgid "“Idaṃ kho no, āvuso ānanda, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.2"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.3"
msgid "yattha jivhā ca nirujjhati, rasasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.4"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ no, āvuso, amhākaṃ acirapakkantassa bhagavato etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.6"
msgid "‘idaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.7"
msgid "“tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.8"
msgid "yattha jivhā ca nirujjhati, rasasaññā ca nirujjhati se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.9"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.10"
msgid "Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.11"
msgid "Tesaṃ no, āvuso, amhākaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.12"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā ānando satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito, sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.13"
msgid "Pahoti cāyasmā ānando imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajituṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.14"
msgid "Yannūna mayaṃ yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkameyyāma; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāmā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:5.15"
msgid "Vibhajatāyasmā ānando”ti. "
msgstr "“May Venerable Ānanda please explain this.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn35.117:6.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, āvuso, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno mahato rukkhassa … pe … "
msgstr "“Reverends, suppose there was a person in need of heartwood. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:6.2"
msgid "vibhajatāyasmā ānando agaruṃ karitvā”ti. "
msgstr "“Please explain this, if it’s no trouble.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.100, sc7
msgctxt "sn35.117:7.1"
msgid "“Tenahāvuso, suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“Then listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:7.2"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato ānandassa paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, reverend,” they replied. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:7.3"
msgid "Āyasmā ānando etadavoca: "
msgstr "Ānanda said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho vo, āvuso, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr "“Reverends, the Buddha gave this brief summary, then entered his dwelling without explaining the meaning in detail: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.2"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr "‘So you should understand that dimension where the eye ceases and perception of sights fades away. You should understand that dimension where the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.3"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti. "
msgstr "mind ceases and perception of thoughts fades away.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.4"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmi. "
msgstr "And this is how I understand the detailed meaning of this summary. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.5"
msgid "Saḷāyatananirodhaṃ no etaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā sandhāya bhāsitaṃ: "
msgstr "The Buddha was referring to the cessation of the six sense fields when he said: "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.6"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe, yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr "‘So you should understand that dimension where the eye ceases and perception of sights fades away. You should understand that dimension where the ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.7"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti. "
msgstr "mind ceases and perception of thoughts fades away.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr "The Buddha gave this brief summary, then entered his dwelling without explaining the meaning in detail. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.9"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.10"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.11"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmi. "
msgstr "And this is how I understand the detailed meaning of this summary. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.117:8.12"
msgid "Ākaṅkhamānā ca pana tumhe āyasmanto bhagavantaṃyeva upasaṅkamatha; "
msgstr "If you wish, you may go to the Buddha and ask him about this. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.13"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ puccheyyātha. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:8.14"
msgid "Yathā vo bhagavā byākaroti tathā naṃ dhāreyyāthā”ti. "
msgstr "You should remember it in line with the Buddha’s answer.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn35.117:9.1"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato ānandassa paṭissutvā uṭṭhāyāsanā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "“Yes, reverend,” replied those mendicants. Then they rose from their seats and went to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.101, sc10
msgctxt "sn35.117:10.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho no, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.2"
msgid "‘tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.3"
msgid "yattha jivhā ca nirujjhati, rasasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.4"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe’ti, tesaṃ no, bhante, amhākaṃ acirapakkantassa bhagavato etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.5"
msgid "‘idaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavā saṅkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.6"
msgid "“tasmātiha, bhikkhave, se āyatane veditabbe yattha cakkhu ca nirujjhati, rūpasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.7"
msgid "yattha mano ca nirujjhati, dhammasaññā ca nirujjhati, se āyatane veditabbe”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.8"
msgid "Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.9"
msgid "Tesaṃ no, bhante, amhākaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.10"
msgid "‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā ānando satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito, sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.11"
msgid "Pahoti cāyasmā ānando imassa bhagavatā saṅkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajituṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.12"
msgid "Yannūna mayaṃ yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkameyyāma; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāmā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.13"
msgid "Atha kho mayaṃ, bhante, yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamimha; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etamatthaṃ paṭipucchimha. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.117:10.14"
msgid "Tesaṃ no, bhante, āyasmatā ānandena imehi ākārehi, imehi padehi, imehi byañjanehi attho vibhatto”ti. "
msgstr "Then they said, “And Ānanda explained the meaning to us in this manner, with these words and phrases.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn35.117:11.1"
msgid "“Paṇḍito, bhikkhave, ānando; mahāpañño, bhikkhave, ānando. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, Ānanda is astute, he has great wisdom. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:11.2"
msgid "Mañcepi tumhe, bhikkhave, etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyātha, ahampi taṃ evamevaṃ byākareyyaṃ yathā taṃ ānandena byākataṃ. "
msgstr "If you came to me and asked this question, I would answer it in exactly the same way as Ānanda. "

msgctxt "sn35.117:11.3"
msgid "Eso cevetassa attho. Evañca naṃ dhāreyyāthā”ti. "
msgstr "That is what it means, and that’s how you should remember it.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.117:11.4"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

